OL,6,FA report investigating how a
OL,7,Fpaedophile headteacher was able to go
OL,8,Fundetected in north Wales and sexually
OL,9,Fabuse girls has been postponed at the
OL,10,Flast minute.
OL,12,FThe year long inquiry into Neil Foden
OL,13,Fwas due to be published by the North
OL,14,FWales Safeguarding Board today but on
OL,15,FTuesday evening a statement was issued
OL,16,Fstating that the Child Practice Review
OL,17,Fwas being postponed while the "board
OL,18,Fconsiders its legal obligations and
OL,19,Finformation sharing further."
