OL,6,FNeil Foden from Old Colwyn is serving
OL,7,F17 years in jail for sexually abusing
OL,8,Ffour girls between 2019 and 2023.
OL,10,FHe was convicted of 19 charges
OL,11,Frelating to four victims, including 12
OL,12,Fcounts of sexual activity with a child.
OL,14,FFor 25 years he ruled his school in
OL,15,FBangor with an iron first but he was
OL,16,Fabusing his position in the community
OL,17,Fto groom and abuse children.
