OL,6,FDuring his trial last year at Mold
OL,7,FCrown court, Judge Rhys Rowlands said
OL,8,Fit was possible that no formal
OL,9,Finvestigation into Foden - despite
OL,10,Fconcerns raised about his behaviour -
OL,11,Femboldened him to continue and he
OL,12,Fcalled him an "arrogant bully".
OL,14,FHe was arrested at Ysgol Friars in
OL,15,FBangor in September 2023 and taken to
OL,16,FCaernarfon police station for
OL,17,Fquestioning and he was later charged.
OL,18,FHe was caught after a young adult
OL,19,Fshowed pictures of Foden on her phone
OL,20,Fand shared conversations she had had
OL,21,Fwith him over a period of six months.
