OL,6,FA Cyngor Gwynedd/ Gwynedd Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We were informed
OL,8,Fat 4:30pm yesterday (23 September) by
OL,9,Fthe North Wales Safeguarding Board
OL,10,Fthat the Child Practice Review report
OL,11,Fwill not be published today, as
OL,12,Fplanned.
OL,14,F"We received no advance notice and
OL,15,Fthere was no discussion with Cyngor
OL,16,FGwynedd about this. We are currently
OL,17,Fawaiting further clarification from
OL,18,Fthe Safeguarding Board.
