OL,6,F"Having waited for the report for so
OL,7,Flong, and preparing to act upon any
OL,8,Fconclusions and recommendations
OL,9,Fwithout delay, we are extremely
OL,10,Fdisappointed that the report will not
OL,11,Fbe published today."
OL,13,FThe North Wales Safeguarding Board
OL,14,Fshared "deepest of regrets" that it
OL,15,Fhad to take the difficult decision to
OL,16,Fdelay publication of the Child
OL,17,FPractice Review 'Our Bravery Brought
OL,18,FJustice' to consider its legal
OL,19,Fobligations and information sharing.
