OL,6,FA statement from the Board said: "We
OL,7,Fappreciate that this is a huge
OL,8,Fdisappointment to all those involved
OL,9,Fnot least the brave women and children
OL,10,Fwho are at the heart of this review.
OL,11,FWe will endeavour to provide a revised
OL,12,Ftimeline as soon as we are able to.
OL,14,F"Those leading on the review continue
